item.title: 【Unreleased/Unofficial (lossless)】FLAC - Beyoncé - COWBOY CARTER (True Immersive 5.1) 16bits 44.1 kHz 6ch
item.description:
Here is the album of the year... For some, hehe.

Beyoncé's studio has not released an immersive version of this album, so my team (not so secret lab) and I have worked on this album for those who wish to experience an immersive version. Disclaimer: the sounds you will hear are not from the studio, they were all extracted with AI (artificial intelligence), so there are probably no new and/or hidden sounds. And last but not least, we do not take requests to remaster other albums.

Feel free to distribute this album in True Immersive, but please do not reuse the sounds to make a Dolby Atmos version and/or other similar audio technologies. Spread the word.

You may need to activate Dolby Atmos on your device...​
